item.title: Webclient Problem [any help?]
item.dc:creator: @deathbysniper97 deathbysniper97
item.description:
@deathbysniper97 wrote:

It would appear to me, and note, this may not be the problem, but it looks like the cache isnt available. Like, if the owner is a good coder, he will know what this means, tell him to re zip the cache, and upload to like, dropbox, and change the cache downloader location in the client to the new place for the cache. There are tons of tutorials telling how to do that, and im not one to search things for people.

I hope i helped you!
